title: March 8, 2025
textContent:
---aftereffects 2.1---

Ang dami na masyado bby di nako makabilang kaya reset na muna HAHAHAHAHA ABABABYU!!

Hehe belated happy anniversary my bby! I'm so happy sa gifts ko! Thank you so much! I appreciate you very much!!! This is the first of our many years together and I'm so so excited on what the future has in store for us niyan! I love you!

Ang ganda ganda rin ng pics naten!! Bagay na bagay talaga tayo nu! Dapat ipost nila yon hmp pag di nila pinost di nako uulit sa kanila hahahaha.

Thank you din bby for making time for our little celebration kahit na naka lamay lolo mo huhu. I appreciate your efforts so much and I'm so lucky that I get to spend time with you!
